testStage.description: Verify that build bubble to Multiconfiguration project is present on Time line on Build History page

steps.name: Click on 'New Item' on the side menu
Click 'Save' button on the BaseConfigPage page
Click 'Logo' button and move to main page
Click 'Build History' on the side menu
Verify that build bubble pop up has job name from header text
